works.description: While we have seen some of the most intricate and impressive luxury watches inspired from the space theme, it seems to the time to take a quick look at those watches that were made on Earth and worn to space by the astronauts. The space age officially began 50 years ago when Russian cosmonaut Yuri Gagarin became the first human to journey into the outer space, and as a tribute, we have listed some of the watches that made their way into the space.
